data.title: IEE Report of Chilime-Trishuli 220 Line and Chilime Substaion PDF
data.meta_description: IEE Report of Chilime-Trishuli 220 Line and Chilime Substaion.pdf - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. This document provides an environmental impact assessment report for the 132/220kV Chilime Substation Hub and Lamjung-Trishuli 220kV transmission line project in Nepal. The report was prepared by the Environmental and Scientific Services Department of the Nepal Electricity Authority. It includes an executive summary in both Nepali and English, a description of the project objectives and components, an analysis of potential environmental impacts, and a review of relevant Nepali policies, regulations and guidelines regarding environmental protection and management.
